Q: Any suggestions before surgery? A: Stock up on pillows, you will basically want to sleep on only pillows.   #BRCA #PDM #ScrewUCancer
Q: Any suggestions before surgery? A: Gel Manicures, you should feel pretty even if you cant move your arms! #BRCA #PDM #ScrewUCancer
Q: Were you in a lot of pain? A: Be sure to take the medication they prescribe, but not all at once.  #BRCA #PDM #ScrewUCancer
Q: How soon after were you able to have sex? A: Be sure to take the medication they prescribe, all at once. #BRCA #PDM #ScrewUCancer
Q: What should I avoid? A: Dogs that jump, and watching too much @ScandalABC #BRCA #PDM #ScrewUCancer
